You need Java 1.6, and a running postgresql8.1 or later server on
localhost.

To set the scoring bot up, invoke ./install.sh .

Edit settings; change the admin password. The admin password is
required when you telnet to localhost, port 8080. (See SETUP for
details)

Then, start ./scoringbot.sh . Connect to localhost with telnet to
port 8080.  Place your testscripts in scripts/ . Make them
executable. A sample is provided.

See SETUP for details on how to create teams and services.

